About

Chris Tyson, known as Chris the Meme God, is a prominent member of MrBeast's team, contributing to the wildly popular YouTube channel known for its elaborate stunts, challenges, and philanthropic efforts. With his humorous and energetic presence, Chris has played a key role in the channel's success. Beyond his work with MrBeast, he has amassed a significant following on social media, where he shares insights into his personal life and interests. In early 2023, Chris publicly came out as gender non-conforming and began hormone replacement therapy (HRT), receiving widespread support from fans and the online community.

HOW TO BUY

Create a Wallet

Download Phantom or your wallet of choice from the app store or google play store for free. Desktop users, download the google chrome extension by going to Phantom.io.

Get Some SOL

Have SOL in your wallet to switch to $GAY. If you dont have any SOL, you can buy directly on Phantom, transfer from another wallet, or buy on another exchange and send it to your wallet.

Go to Raydium

Connect to Raydium. Go to raydium.io in google chrome or on the browser inside your Phantom app. Connect your wallet. Paste the $GAY token address into Raydium, select Chase, and confirm. When Phantom prompts you for a wallet signature, sign.

Swap SOL for $GAY

Swap SOL for $GAY. We have ZERO taxes so you dont need to worry about buying with a specific slippage, although you may need to use slippage during times of market volatility.
